These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Job: manager, pilot, lawyer, dressmaker
Nationality: mexican, chinese, argentine, italian
1. Nationality:italian is on the left of Job:lawyer##1
2. Job:manager is on the left of Nationality:chinese##1
3. Job:dressmaker is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:argentine is on the left or right of Nationality:italian##3
5. Job:manager is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Job   | manager | pilot | dressmaker | lawyer |
| Nationality        | mexican | chinese   | italian | argentine    |

