.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Color: black, apricot, blood-red, coral
Hobby: filmmaking, puzzles, collecting, dancing
1. Color:apricot is on the left of Color:coral##1
2. Hobby:filmmaking is on the left of Hobby:collecting##1
3. Hobby:collecting is in an odd position##4
4. Hobby:filmmaking == Color:black##1
5. Hobby:puzzles is on the right of Hobby:collecting##1
6. Hobby:filmmaking == Color:black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Color   | blood-red | black  | apricot  | coral |
| Hobby   | dancing    | filmmaking | collecting | puzzles    |

