.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Flower: lily, iris, marigold, poppy
Color: purple, mauve, emerald, azure
1. Flower:poppy is on the left or right of Color:azure##3
2. Flower:marigold is in an even position##4
3. Color:azure is on the left or right of Flower:iris##3
4. Color:azure is on the right of Color:emerald##1
5. Color:purple is in an odd position##4
6. Flower:iris is on the right of Flower:marigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Flower          | poppy | marigold | iris    | lily      |
| Color   | emerald        | azure     | purple | mauve |

