Cigar: old-henry, blend, baccarat, siglo
1. Transport:snowmobile is between Cigar:old-henry and Cigar:siglo##2
2. Transport:ship is on the left of Transport:quad-bike##1
3. Cigar:baccarat is in an odd position##4
4. Cigar:blend is on the left of Cigar:siglo##1
5. Cigar:blend is on the right of Transport:quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Transport         | ship | quad-bike | snowmobile | taxi |
| Cigar   | baccarat       | old-henry   | blend    | siglo  |

